---
title: Sticky Beef & Veggie Udon Stir-Fry with Crispy Shallots
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan for a sweet chilli and oyster sauce mix that can take a beef and veggie stir-fry to stardom. Sealing this stir-fry’s rightful place are udon noodles - we give it a gold star for sure!

